  ('dietitian-moex-10579', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關oxidized LDL的敘述，何者為非？', '["macrophage攝入oxidized LDL比攝入正常的LDL更快速", "oxidized LDL會誘導macrophage進入次內皮組織之間", "oxidized LDL會抑制macrophage的移動性，造成macrophage堆積於內皮組織", "oxidized LDL是發生於LDL脂質的double bond的過氧化反應"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b924a8f44c2", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094130", "c": "112", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
